Scotland Yard said the Homicide and Major Crime Command has been informed and inquiries have begun.

No arrests have been made and the next of kin are yet to be informed.

A post-mortem examination will be held in due course.

Anyone with information is asked to contact police via 101 or Crimestoppers anonymously on 0800 555 111.

